# AI DDR Report Generator

This project builds an AI-powered system to generate a Detailed Diagnostic Report (DDR) from inspection and thermal PDFs.

## 🚀 Features
- Extracts data from inspection & thermal reports
- Uses LLM to structure and analyze issues
- Merges insights into a final DDR report

## ▶️ How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Add your API key in `.env`:
   GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

3. Run:
   python main.py

## 📄 Output
The system generates:
- final_report.txt

